<P>
17-YEAR-OLD NORMAN WILLOVER TELLS KCBA HE HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH A TWO-HOUR CRIME SPREE THAT TOOK THE LIVES OF TWO PENINSULA WOMEN.
<P>
IN FACT. HE SAYS HE WAS SET UP.
<P>
CHERI GYURO IS FOLLOWING THE STORY.SHE JOINS US LIVE FROM THE NEWS DESK WITH ALL THE INFORMATION. WHAT DID WILLOVER SAY?
<P>

