<A NAME=107Willover - i>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Willover - i</H3><BR>
ALAN, WILLOVER CALLED FROM JUVENILE HALL TODAY.ASKING TO SPEAK TO A KCBA REPORTER.
<P>
HE SAID HE WANTED TO GIVE HIS SIDE OF THE STORY.
<P>
WILLOVER IS ACCUSED OF SHOOTING AND KILLING TWO WOMEN AND INJURING A THIRD IN FEBRUARY.    
<P>
BUT WILLOVER SAYS HE WAS NOWHERE NEAR EITHER CRIME SCENES THE NIGHT OF THE MURDERS.
<P>

