<A NAME=108Willover - g>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Willover - g</H3><BR>
NORMAN WILLOVER CALLED KCBA FROM JUVENILE HALL SAYING HE WANTS THE PUBLIC TO KNOW HIS SIDE OF THE STORY.
<P>
WILLOVER AND 19-YEAR-OLD JOE MANIBUSAN ARE ACCUSED OF SHOOTING 35-YEAR-OLD PRIYA MATHEWS AND 27-YEAR-OLD JENNIFER ANINGER IN MONTEREY.THEN SHOOTING 47-YEAR-OLD FRANCES OLIVIO IN SEASIDE.ALL IN THE SAME NIGHT.
<P>
MATHEWS AND OLIVIO BOTH DIED.
<P>
WILLOVER SAYS HE WAS NOT INVOLVED IN THE SHOOTINGS.AND THAT HE WAS NOT IN THE VEHICLE WHERE THE SHOTS WERE FIRED.
<P>
BUT HE DOES SAY MONTEREY POLICE ARRESTED HIM FOR RUNNING AWAY FROM A GROUP HOME IN UTAH.AND FORCED HIM TO CONFESS TO THE SHOOTINGS.
<P>
WILLOVER SAYS THE POLICE CAME TO HIS HOUSE BEFORE THE SHOOTING ONCE.INJECTED TRUTH SYRUM IN HIM.AND TRIED TO FORCE HIM TO CONFESS TO A ROBBERY AT THE GALAXY THEATRE.
<P>
HE SAYS HE WAS NOT ARRESTED FOR THAT CRIME.BUT HE SAYS POLICE PLOTTED AGAINST HIM TO GET INCRIMINATING EVIDENCE AGAINST HIM FOR THE MURDERS.
<P>
"WE SPOKE WITH WILLOVER'S ATTORNEY.JOHN HOWELL.HE DIDN'T WANT TO APPEAR ON CAMERA.BUT HE DID SAY THAT WILLOVER ONCE EXPRESSED A DESIRE TO SPEAK WITH THE MEDIA.HOWELL SAYS HE DISCOURAGED THAT."
<P>
HOWELL TOLD KCBA QUOTE: "HE HAS A HISTORY OF MENTAL ABERRATION.  HE'S DISTURBED, HE SHOULDN'T BE TALKING TO THE MEDIA."  HE ALSO SAID QUOTE: "HE'S A SERIOUSLY DISTURBED PERSON.DOCTORS WHO EVALUATED HIM SAY HE IS IN NEED OF PSYCHIATRIC HELP IN A LOCKED FACILITY."
<P>
WILLOVER ADMITS HE'S HAD PROBLEMS WITH THE LAW IN THE PAST.
<P>
WILLOVER ADMITS.HE'S HAD TROUBLE WITH THE LAW IN THE PAST.
<P>

